# Push workflow (SMB Health Supply)

When the user says **push**, they mean both:

1. **GitHub** — commit changes, push to `origin` on the default branch
2. **Vercel** — deploy production (`vercel deploy --prod` from `site/`, or rely on Vercel Git integration if a push triggers deploy)

Do not push to only one unless the user explicitly asks for GitHub-only or Vercel-only.

Repository: `lowdifficulty/smb-health-supply`
Deploy directory: `site/`
